### **4. 21_LiveMetricCanvas**  
**Description:**  
A real-time visualization tool for plotting incoming numeric data streams.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveMetricCanvas - Real-Time Data Plot Tool

LiveMetricCanvas helps visualize simulations, sensor input, or API metrics as live, scrollable line charts.

## Features
- Real-time updates  
- Smooth line animation  
- Simple and clean UI  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/21_LiveMetricCanvas.git
cd 21_LiveMetricCanvas
python visualize.py
